id: pm-xnkd
title: "pm close --duplicate-of: structured duplicate tracking with auto-populated closure fields (GH-183, GH-160)"
description: "Add --duplicate-of <id> to pm close: validates target exists and is not itself closed-as-duplicate, sets duplicate_of metadata on the closed item, auto-populates resolution/expected_result/actual_result (suppressing close_validation_missing_fields warnings), standardizes the close reason, and adds a comment on the canonical item. Fixes GitHub issues #183 and #160."
